To fetch your API Access Token, please login to the Newsbreak Admanager Platform. Click on Tools - Resources - API Access Tokens. Here you can click 'Generate token' to create your own API access token. Please remember that this token is tied to your user ID and should not be shared with anyone else.

To integrate multiple events in one account with RedTrack, you will need to set up postbacks for each event. Unfortunately, I don't have a specific guide for RedTrack integration. However, you can refer to our generic postback integration guide for more details on how to set up postbacks. You can find it here: [API Integration Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/27680147056397-API-Integration-Guide).
